name: do busão
description: this is a fragment from the photo series "paths and talks" taken from inside of a busao (we call bus "busao" in brazil like a caring nickname for public transport that makes part of life of so many of us) while i was in my way to work. this scene is so common in everyday life that we don't pay attention to so many elements that cross our path. also there is the charming little blur in the right side.
